title.narrative: Support programme for the energy sector in Cuba - Energy efficiency

description.narrative: The Support programme for energy eff. in Cuba (the full title is "Support programme for the energy sector in Cuba - Energy efficiency") is part of the larger "Support Programme for the Energy Sector in Cuba" funded by the European Union and jointly implemented by UNDP and UNIDO. UNIDO is responsible for work on Energy Efficiency. UNDP is responsible for work on Renewable Energy. The project is implemented through/with the intermediation of the Multi-Partner Trust Fund Office (MPTF Office).
